Description_lang: Your spells and abilities have a high chance to impale your target with a spike of Azerite, causing ${$m1*(1+$@versadmg)*(1+($295836m1/100))} Fire damage.

description_blz.en_US: Your spells and abilities have a high chance to impale your target with a spike of Azerite, causing 64 Fire damage.

description_blz.de_DE: Eure Zauber und Fähigkeiten haben eine hohe Chance, das Ziel mit einem Azeritstachel aufzuspießen, der ihm 64 Feuerschaden zufügt.

description_blz.ko_KR: 주문과 능력 사용 시 높은 확률로 대상을 아제라이트 가시로 꿰뚫어 64의 화염 피해를 입힙니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 你的法術和技能有很高的機率以艾澤萊晶岩刺貫穿目標，造成64點火焰傷害。
